<main role="main" class="inner cover app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h2 class="cover-heading">About Me</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "Profile.jpg", width: 250, alt: "Profile image", class: "profile-img" %>
        
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4> 
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>% "
                >
                </div>
              </div>              
            </div>         
          <% end %>
        </div>      
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p class="lead">I'm a self tought developer with over an year of experience in Ruby on Rails Programming. So far in my journey I have build two complete Rails applications with a vast array of functionality and deployed a RubyGem that has been downloaded more than 250 times. I'm comfortable incorporating RubyGems as well as styling with Bootstrap 4.4. </p> 
        <p class="lead">I'm interested in further my carreer in developing and I am planning to  expand my knowlege in PHP as well as in Python. My schedule is very flexible and I am looking forward to assit you in any capacity to fullfill your developing needs </p>
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              List of Jobs I was Employed at Uber, PNC, Metlife, Our Lady of Mercy, USC+LAC, UBOC, WF
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              List of Jobs I was Employed at Uber, PNC, Metlife, Our Lady of Mercy, USC+LAC, UBOC, WF
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Udemy: Dissecting Ruby on Rails, Complete Ruby on Rails
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              SGUSOM: Grenada, West Indies
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </div> 
</main>
